main event: A UFO was observed moving in the sky near Roscoe, New York on August 12, 1961.
interesting points: The sighting lasted for 15 minutes., The UFO was reported to be maneuvering through the sky., Observations indicate the object exhibited rapid movements and sudden changes of direction., The Air Force received the report for further investigation., No photographs were included with the sighting report.
witness description: Civilian who observed a strange object in the sky.
